snippet.title: Nintendo Switch - Curse Crackers: For Whom the Belle Toils - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Curse Crackers: For Whom the Belle Toils is an acrobatic 2D platformer where you play as Belle and her companion Chime, jumping, vaulting and swinging your way through levels in a world inspired by classic handheld games. Chase down Bonnie and her crew of troublemakers to get your boyfriend back!
Coming August 24th
#cursecrackers #nintendoswitch #eshop
